title: War of the Roses: To Keep Her Wax Appointment, That is the Question
description: McKayla has been seeing Jeremy but he basically only talks to her when he wants to.  She wants to know if he's seeing anyone else because she wants to cancel her next wax appointment if he is.  McKayla doesn't want to waste her money and go through the pain if Jeremy isn't putting her first.
